channel.title: Need Someone to Upload Me a Basic Webclient
channel.description:
Hi guys, I've been trying to upload a client for ages and I just can't get it. I've found myself a coder, and he's currently working on a server for me, (Project Insanity source) but we don't have enough money to afford a VPS yet. Could anyone upload a quick temporary server onto rs-ps.or/g for me? Just a plain Project Insanity spawn with some basic stuff done to it. I'm asking for something quick and small, I'm not looking for anything crazy. So please, if you think you can upload one for me, just shoot me an Email at:
evolutionpkrsps@aol.com
Please include a way for me to contact you back.
Thanks for your time,
Anthony
